Class SelectionGraphOption<T>

java.lang.Object
seng202.group2.view.graphs.GraphOption
seng202.group2.view.graphs.SelectionGraphOption<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the objects between which the user may select.
public class SelectionGraphOption<T>
extends GraphOption
A GraphOption used for displaying a list of choices to the user, out of which the user chooses one.
Author:
Connor Dunlop
